OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fstart heavy in the east but will ease
OL,7,Fa little tonight, but it will remain
OL,8,Fcloudy and mild with outbreaks of
OL,9,Fdrizzle. Winds will strengthen in the
OL,10,Ffar west. Fog forming over the hills.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA spell of heavy rain and
OL,13,Fblustery winds will move through on
OL,14,FWednesday morning, followed by drier
OL,15,Fand brighter weather with isolated
OL,16,Fshowers. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
